approveRequest(uint256).details: This function iterates through all organs, finds one that is not assigned, has been consented to, evaluated, stored, but still available, updates the corresponding OrganId struct with the new donor information and emits an event indicating approval of a request. It also increments or decrements counters as needed.

params.requestId: The unique identifier of the request being approved.
